Usage: SET STATUS_CHANVOICE <text of display for status line voice mode>
  The value of STATUS_CHANVOICE is replaced in the STATUS_FORMAT
  variable for any occurence of %- if you have channel voice status.
  If you are a chanop or not voiced, %- is replaced with nothing.

See Also:  
  SET STATUS_CHANOP
